commit.message: CI: bump actions/checkout to @main
Specs: remove each_key tests from more standard tests

File: fix jruby issue with File#rename

For some reason it clobbers permissions on dest directories
File: fix each_key and add security around path names
Specs: remove with_each_key from standard stores

Transforms::BEncode: raise error if deserialize returns nil

BEncode can't encode nil values, so this can never happen

Specs: add better each_key test

The existing each_key tests didn't test enough key types
Update FILES
Moneta: add serialize_keys_unless_string option

Transforms: restore behaviour of key serializers

In the previous implementation key transforms that were considered
"serializers" only transformed keys that weren't strings already.

Technically this should have meant that key enumeration on all of these
transforms should not have been allowed.
Transforms::UUEncode: fix mixed up encode/decode
Transforms::Truncate: fix initializer
Transforms::Hex: use unpack1
Transforms::QP: fix mixed up pack/unpack
Transformer: recover from errors thrown decoding each_key
Transform: raise NotImplementedError for missing methods
Specs: modify each_key+prefix checks & move to a different location
Transformer: remove old transformer code
